<content5 releasenbr="1">
<step1>
<ptxt>CONSTRUCTION</ptxt>
<step2>
<ptxt>Vane Pump Assembly</ptxt>
<step3>
<ptxt>A compact and lightweight vane pump, which uses die-cast aluminum as the material for its housing, is used.</ptxt>
</step3>
<step3>
<ptxt>A belt drive type vane pump with a built-in reservoir tank is used.</ptxt>
